General.Name: UMS Holdings Bhd
General.Description: UMS Holdings Berhad, an investment holding company, markets and distributes mechanical power transmission and material handling products and systems, and industrial spare parts in Malaysia and Singapore. It offers rubber conveyor belts; portable dry vapour steam cleaning equipment; filtration solutions; conveyor belts; belt fasteners, cleaners, and maintenance products; conveyor chains and power transmission products; fluid sealing and pipeline solutions; modular plastic and ThermoDrive belting products; steel and plastic chains and components; industrial and automotive belts; power transmission, clamping fixtures, and remote control systems; rolling bearings; standard chains with solid bushings and rollers; conveyor belt trackers and misalignment solutions; fluid couplings; and fabric and steel cord conveyor belts, as well as products that clean, wash, disinfect, degrease, lubricate, polish, and protect workplace and home. The company also provides lubricants and grease solution; hand and power tools; and wrench, hex key, plier, screwdriver, and socket products, as well as automotive and general tools. It serves palm oil, rubber, power generation, quarrying and cement industries, latex glove manufacturing, and electrical and electronic industries. The company was founded in 1941 and is headquartered in Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia.
